\newlabel{fig:fillall}{{11}{22}{\textbf {Fill All Months} tab in its initial state. The left sidebar shows the \textit {Active Mappings} panel with \textbf {All} and \textbf {None} toggle buttons for selecting which mapping types to include. On the right, set the \textit {Year} and \textit {Target Month}, then click \textbf {Scan Files} to discover all source files from January through the target month. The \textit {Execute Fill All Months} button becomes active after a successful scan}{figure.11}{}}
